video.title: Go! Live Your Way
video.synopsis: Charismatic Mía gets a scholarship to an elite performing arts school, where she makes close friends but clashes with the owner's popular daughter.

episodes.synopsis: Energetic singer-dancer Mía auditions for Saint Mary, a fancy boarding school with a performing arts department. Popular Lupe dislikes her instantly.
episodes.title: Episode 1

episodes.synopsis: An upset and rejected Juanma tries to leave Saint Mary. Mía's godmother takes her to school, but Mercedes is confused about why she's there.
episodes.title: Episode 2

episodes.synopsis: Mía convinces new friends Zoe and Simón to try out for Go! Agus asks Sofía for boy advice, and Álvaro suspects Juanma is playing badly on purpose.
episodes.title: Episode 3

episodes.synopsis: Lupe tries to get Mía in trouble with a video while Juanma makes Álvaro miss the basketball game. Ramiro remembers Mía's talented mother.
episodes.title: Episode 4

episodes.synopsis: Lupe hosts her exclusive annual back-to-school party, but it's Mía who has to save the day with music, energy -- and an old friend.
episodes.title: Episode 5

episodes.synopsis: Mía has a stressful dance-off with Lupe before getting to know Álvaro better. Juanma tries to apologize for his actions.
episodes.title: Episode 6

episodes.synopsis: Mercedes wants to fix things between Juanma and Lupe. Mía fights with Gaspar about the band and gets into trouble over her grades.
episodes.title: Episode 7

episodes.synopsis: Lupe tells Mía they should be friends, Olivia shares her feelings with Álvaro, and Zoe secretly meets up with Gaspar.
episodes.title: Episode 8

episodes.synopsis: Mía gets upset with Álvaro for talking to Gaspar about a Saint Mary scholarship. Agus is worried her secret crush will find out she likes him.
episodes.title: Episode 9

episodes.synopsis: Álvaro's dad forces him to do a big interview instead of playing in an important basketball game ... but Mía has other plans.
episodes.title: Episode 10

episodes.synopsis: Lupe is upset about Ivana's choice for soloist, and her parents get into a fight about it. Meanwhile, Juanma deals with his injury.
episodes.title: Episode 11

episodes.synopsis: Álvaro tells Juanma not to hurt his sister, Mía gets jealous of Olivia, and Gaspar is worried about his scholarship application.
episodes.title: Episode 12

episodes.synopsis: Álvaro's father visits the school. Lupe wants to change her duet with Zoe, and Juanma makes a decision about his new activity.
episodes.title: Episode 13

episodes.synopsis: Lupe's jealousy and competitiveness with Mía has her acting out -- just as an important competition is about to start.
episodes.title: Episode 14

episodes.synopsis: The Go! team competes with their song and dance numbers. But many surprises -- both good and bad -- happen during their dynamic performances.
episodes.title: Episode 15

episodes.synopsis: Mía asks Ramiro if he had a relationship with her mother. Álvaro worries about changing schools. The students sing goodbye to a teacher.
episodes.title: Episode 1

episodes.synopsis: Zoe confronts Lupe about her actions, and Álvaro and Olivia get to know each other better. Mía looks for clues in a love letter.
episodes.title: Episode 2

episodes.synopsis: Mía helps Lupe with her dance moves before Natasha chooses the group performances. Álvaro decides what to do about Olivia's crush.
episodes.title: Episode 3

episodes.synopsis: Álvaro and Juanma are devastated to learn Mía is moving -- but Lupe celebrates. Zoe and Gaspar's relationship is revealed.
episodes.title: Episode 4

episodes.synopsis: Mía's friends bid her a tearful -- and musical -- farewell. Lupe tries to impress a famous music producer at an ice cream shop.
episodes.title: Episode 5

episodes.synopsis: When music producer Charly Martin hosts singing auditions at the school, Lupe attempts to sabotage Mía in order to win.
episodes.title: Episode 6

episodes.synopsis: The new Go! instructor hosts auditions for male performers. Juanma and Mía's personal life gets in the way of recording their duet.
episodes.title: Episode 7

episodes.synopsis: Ramiro gets the DNA test results back. Álvaro's feelings for Mía threaten to ruin his basketball game. Lupe's mischief continues.
episodes.title: Episode 8

episodes.synopsis: Álvaro plans a special dinner for Mía. Martín wants to get back at Tobí. Mercedes and her friend do their own DNA test.
episodes.title: Episode 9

episodes.synopsis: Lupe looks for a way to eliminate Juanma and Mía from nationals. Zoe and Simón wonder about their friendship.
episodes.title: Episode 10

episodes.synopsis: Juanma and Mía must decide between Go! and their professional careers. Ramiro asks Isabel for answers. Lupe feels lonely.
episodes.title: Episode 11

episodes.synopsis: Álvaro tries hard to find a way to get Juanma to rejoin the basketball team. Fede wants Sofí to trust him.
episodes.title: Episode 12

episodes.synopsis: Help springs from a surprising source when Lupe finds out her parents are separating. Mía is torn between Juanma and Álvaro.
episodes.title: Episode 13

episodes.synopsis: Mía makes her choice while Lupe discovers startling news. Simón has a technical problem with the team's music right before nationals.
episodes.title: Episode 14

episodes.synopsis: The Go! singers compete in nationals against unexpected rivals while Mía, Lupe and Álvaro deal with their new reality.
episodes.title: Episode 15
